channel.title: Help with playing MoparScape!
channel.description:
I need help with playing MoparScape and I am on my mom's Computer usually it works on mine but when I try to play it on this one a Pretty Rex X comes up. And my mom won't let me download anything.
Thing's I've tried:
Disableing FireWall
Updating Java
Pressing Accept when the thing comes up and asks if you trust it
Allowing everything on Internet Explorer
Allowing everything on FireFox
Trying the game on FireFox and Internet Explorer
(What else should I do??)
[br][size=1]Posted at: October 01, 2006, 03:50:01 PM[/size][hr]I need more suggestions! I really want to play!!
